05:35.545 --> 05:39.298
This is the mark of rain,
nature's greatest asset.

05:39.715 --> 05:43.177
It has the power to give life,
and to take it away.

05:45.805 --> 05:49.308
And this sun is you, little Samurai,

05:49.976 --> 05:54.188
